covid_banner.38540: At Tropical Smoothie Cafe, our mission is to inspire a healthier lifestyle. Our mission extends well beyond simply offering delicious food and smoothies - we care deeply about the health and well-being of our guests inside and outside of our cafes. With recent events, we feel it's important to share what precautions we're taking to help address Coronavirus (COVID-19) concerns among our guests, crew members and communities across the country. Effective immediately, all Tropical Smoothie Cafe locations are following a closed dining room policy.  In some circumstances, you can still enter and place your order, but we ask that you consume all products off-premise.  We will be packaging all orders as carryout. We are still open for online ordering and delivery, and look forward to serving you in those platforms. Additionally, our incredible franchise owners have educated crew members on the symptoms of COVID-19 and how it spreads, and have increased the cleaning and sanitizing procedures for their cafes. In some cases, your local cafe may close temporarily for a deeper cleaning, but it will continue carryout and delivery service as soon as practical. We are continuing to closely monitor Centers for Disease Control and Prevention (CDC) and work with local health departments to track the latest developments and updated guidance to ensure we're always prioritizing our guests. Please visit www.tropicalsmoothiecafe.com for more information.
